 <span class="px-2 text-gray-600">/</span>
 <span class="text-gold-500">Custom Polo Shirts</span>
 </nav>

 <span class="mb-3 inline-block font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gold-500">Branded Apparel</span>
